title: $ to LP Staking tutorial page
body:
There is a bit of research needed to get setup.
This is an entry to barrier that can be easily addressed.
it would help to have a step by step tutorial or link to a tutorial.

[1] Mouse-over '?' widget on the 'Select your Mutant' page with a link to information on using Uniswap and LP token staking. 

[2] Tutorial page medium article, paragraphs, screenshots, GIFs. 
'get started' or 'tutorial' button on top bar of ymen.finance

[3] New people should figure it out without our help.

This vote does not guarantee any changes discussed. Symbolic vote on community opinion only. 2 week poll.
choices: New people should figure it out without our help.
author: 0x225D29eb77a18a7E520c9bB431c5bd8B1bE376A5
